                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1628-18500916 t18500916-1628-punishment-64"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>(There were three other indictments against the prisoner.)</p>
